<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l1"><expan>Hılpolt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Prunn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der geltſchuld </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l3"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Jr vns nach des <expan>ſchuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ſag den wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l4">ewch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . becʒalt ſolt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ wır darinn ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l5"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l6">vns das niht füklıch ıſt wan vns dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe dıe ſach antrıft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l7"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>anlıg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd getrawn ewch wol daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l8">das nıht für v̈bel habt vnd ſchıkt daʒ wır becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> vvan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l9">vns nıht lıeb <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>ſölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>bürg<ex>en</ex></expan> nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> ſag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l10"><expan>ʒuſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l11">Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch vormals ʒwyr <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> daʒ <expan>Abraha<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l12">Jud von <expan>Münche<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns ſprıcht / daʒ er <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wıſſ . Doch hett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l13">Jr ʒu Jm ıht <expan>ʒuſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo well er eẅch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l14"><expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewalt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>Recht<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l15">vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . dabey meint der Jud ʒe <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>VVan<ex>n</ex></expan> auch ſıe des von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l16"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> küng alſo gefreyt ſınd / Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l18">wo wir eẅch ſuſt lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l17"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l19"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Barbare . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hilpolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Prunn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der geltschuld
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir uns nach des
                                <expan>schuldbr<ex>iefs</ex></expan> sag, den wir
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von ewch
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, beczalt solt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz wir darinn ein
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan> tun <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz
                        uns das niht füklich ist, wan uns die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die
                        die sach antrift, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>anlig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und
                        getrawn ewch wol, daz ir uns das niht für übel habt und schikt, daz wir
                        beczalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> wan uns niht lieb
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan>
<expan>sölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bürg<ex>en</ex></expan> nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> sag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>zusprech<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan>; denn
                        als ir uns aber <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des juden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch vormals zwyr <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t,</expan> daz
                                <expan>Abraha<ex>m</ex></expan>, jud von
                            <expan>Münche<ex>n</ex></expan>, bey uns spricht, daz er
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wiss. Doch hett ir zu im iht
                            <expan>zu sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>, so well er ewch
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> sein vor des reichs
                                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. Dabey meint der jud ze
                                <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> auch
                        sie des von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> küng,
                        also gefreyt sind; denn wo wir ewch sust lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Barbare. </ab>
</div>
